after perishing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  [Hence also,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A return to the fight, after wheeling away,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"retiring:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and simply,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a charge,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an assault,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in war;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kur~aY","text_ar":"كُرَّى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Sgh, K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kar~aAtN","text_ar":"كَرَّاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b4-  [Hence also,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A time; one time;"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the sense of the French"},{"kind":"text","text":"“"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fois"},{"kind":"text","text":"”; generally repeated, or used in the pl. form, so as to denote a returning to an action, once, or more; i. e., repetition, or reiteration, thereof, agreeably with the primary signification;] syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mar~apN","text_ar":"مَرَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) pl. as above. (S.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEalahu kar~apF baEoda kar~apK","text_ar":"فَعَلَهُ كَرَّةً بَعْدَ كَرَّةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did it time after time"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEalahu kar~aAtK","text_ar":"فَعَلَهُ كَرَّاتٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did it several times"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b5-  [Hence also,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A turn to prevail against an opposing party; victory."},{"kind":"text","text":"So in the Kur, [xvii. 6,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vum~a radadonaA lakumu","text_ar":"ثُمَّ رَدَدْنَا لَكُمُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alkar~apa Ealayohimo","text_ar":"الكَرَّةَ عَلَيْهِمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Then we gave to you the turn to prevail against them; the victory over them"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Bd, Jel.)"}],"source_refs":["Mgh","K","Sgh","S"]}]}}